--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This package facilitates running Google's Gemma family of models (Gemma 4 E2B,
E4B; Gemma 3, etc.) on-device. The model weights themselves are NOT bundled in
this package and are downloaded separately from HuggingFace
(litert-community/gemma-4-*-it-litert-lm).

Gemma model weights are governed by the Gemma Terms of Use:

  https://ai.google.dev/gemma/terms

Downstream applications that ship Gemma weights must comply with the Gemma
Prohibited Use Policy:

  https://ai.google.dev/gemma/prohibited_use_policy

Distribution and use of Gemma model weights is the responsibility of the
consuming application, not this package.
